	will be presented in 4 iterations over 5 weeks\, with one week off.\n\nThi
	s is a four-session course recurring on Wednesdays from 6-9 PM. Students w
	ill gain familiarity with all aspects of tracking a band and delivering a 
	mixed product. Online resources will accompany the in-person sessions\, so
	 participants can gain familiarity with the professional audio software RE
	APER. Upon completion of the course\, students should have a basic underst
	anding of Vera studio operations and are eligible to rent the space after 
	a competency test.\n\nThe class dates are as follows:\n\n- Wed\, February 
	4\, 6-9 PM\n- Wed\, February 11\, 6-9 PM\n- NO CLASS on Wednesday February
	 17\n- Wed\, February 25\, 6-9 PM\n- Wed\, March 4\, 6-9 PM\n\nhttps://lin
	k.dice.fm/Bed494310331\n\nFrom The Vera Project
