UID:z0C6-QG53VHxTv-dHnveW
SUMMARY:ILUKA: The Wings Tour w/ Fern Spores
DTSTAMP:20260301T153235Z
DTSTART:20260302T040000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $15 ($20.09 after fees)\n\nDay of: $18 ($26.27 after f
	ees)\n\nILUKA:\n\nAustralian singer-songwriter ILUKA returns to her homela
	nd from Los Angeles on her first global tour in support of her new album\,
	 the wild\, the innocent\, & the raging. A fierce celebration of individua
	lity\, womanhood\, and defiance\, the album embraces ILUKA’s unapologetic 
	honesty — a quality that has defined her as one of alt-pop’s most vital di
	sruptors. ILUKA isn’t afraid to be outspoken\, share her feelings\, let ou
	t a little rage\, or get weird. This unabashed honesty underscores her art
	istry as she stretches the boundaries of pop with blunt lyrics sweetened b
	y disarmingly catchy songcraft and a bewitching aesthetic.\n\nPlease note\
	, the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 21+ bar and venue and does not accept ve
	rtical ID’s for entry.\n\nhttps://link.dice.fm/M53eb37615b1\n\nFrom Sunset
	 Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/M53eb37615b1
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
