	e way. BBH has toured with The Beths\, Margaret Glaspy\, The Front Bottoms
	\, Hippo Campus\, and Michelle Branch\, among many others. Their fourth al
	bum Bad Bad Hats will be released April 12\, 2024 on Don Giovanni Records.
